60
00:07:35,014 --> 00:07:40,779
<i>Eighty-seven days later Adaline
married Clarence James Prescott,</i>

61
00:07:40,829 --> 00:07:44,834
<i>at Old Saint Mary's
Cathedral in San Francisco.</i>

62
00:07:47,792 --> 00:07:52,887
<i>Three years later Adaline
gave birth to a baby girl.</i>

63
00:07:53,274 --> 00:07:58,540
<i>They named her Fleming,
